Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:06.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,衰弱 贫困 贫富差距变大…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就是暗黑年代的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这看不到未来的时代里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女神们降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:20.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们用可爱的笑容和歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:23.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,改变深陷泥潭的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:26.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:31.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:45.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哇 360度都是大海!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:47.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 我们不是来玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:51.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 和东京很不一样 很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:56.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 那个形状  我看见猫岛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:59.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神代先生 猫岛是怎么样的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,概括的说 就是因猫多而出名的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,据说那里猫和人以理想的形式共存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:09.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可以作为今后社会建设模型的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:14.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,数量真多啊  感觉一下船就会被猫包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:19.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫岛的孩子们的来信上写的东西都是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:23.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,岛上的猫都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:27.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员 请帮帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:30.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然这样说 但是还是有猫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊… 一只猫也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们是女主角党的各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很感谢你们大老远的过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我家的猫 马卡龙和花花不见了 不知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:51.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我家的胡桃和坚果也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是你们写的信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:54.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫怎么会不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个…我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快点儿! 别磨磨蹭蹭的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,干嘛停在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:09.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快上岸啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是猫嶋议员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫嶋议员?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是出身于这个岛的国会议员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:20.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 她非常讨厌猫 就算我们给她写了信 她也没有采取任何措施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:24.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是一直把偶像议员当成眼中钉的那位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没想到会在这种地方遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,屋顶之间的木板是给猫走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:33.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,道路上的标记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是给猫让路的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个牌子是给车看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真厉害 大家都很喜欢猫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:52.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那是猫里面最厉害的猫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,它在岛上巡视其他的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在岛上只剩下猫老大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,摸了它就会有好事发生 被岛上的人当成神明供奉着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:05.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在岛上的猫都不见了 它不高兴所以不让人碰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 有庆典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯 是岛上最大的庆典活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫大浪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:20.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很多猫聚集在一起 从起点一起跑到终点的庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫像巨浪一样涌过来 大家都被猫簇拥着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:27.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:32.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为猫不见了 这次的庆典没法举行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:37.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别担心 姐姐们会想办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一起猫上身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫上身…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然说了要帮忙解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是连猫影子也没见着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:29.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是樱子和五十铃啊 你们好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那两位是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星光党的饭塚樱子和鸣神五十铃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 和我们一样也是偶像议员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是 新当选的议员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 我是星菜夏月 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是饭塚樱子 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,白雪 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,白雪 你也来打个招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那位是绫井白雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她出身于乌冬县
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这汤 真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:09.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,话说回来 樱子你们也收到信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:16.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哪里需要我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不论多远我们也会赶赴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,完美的偶像笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不愧是星光党的领队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,樱子 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,游艇被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个时节会有古怪的海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这下糟了 回去的时候得买新船才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呀……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快去追船啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,白雪也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,魔鬼静也有怕的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:16.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好好拴住船的话 一眨眼它就会被冲到海面上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶您很熟悉这个岛上的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:25.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我只是活了很久 很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:28.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶被称为岛上的活字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,岛上的什么事她都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您从很久以前就一直在这里做乌冬面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:41.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,四名少女出现在海的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在猫的石舞台上起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:48.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很久 很久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很久以前流传下来的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有猫的岛 真是太舒服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个岛的观光资源只有猫 猫都消失了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就没人来这个岛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫是我在这个世上最讨厌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小的时候 周围都是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,它们是过的舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我可就很悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,它们那傲慢的脸和态度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,光是看到就心烦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:37.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,找了这么久还没找到猫 是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明天问问岛上的人有没有头绪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,到底去哪儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,试试问问猫老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,和它一起玩的话一定会告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫老大会告诉我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,姐姐 跟我们一起去好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,天快黑啦 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:04.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠姐 明天可以跟孩子们一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可以 我和静去问岛上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你和孩子们调查完 我们再汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天先回家 明天去找猫老大玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你到底要吃几碗才够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一直在吃乌冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不愧是白雪推荐的乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,吃了这个乌冬能让人感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您是从什么时候开始做这乌冬的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从很久很久以前就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫不见了 岛上的人都很愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎样才能把猫召唤回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:50.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用这个暖暖的飞鱼高汤乌冬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,肯定会上瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫舌头吃不了热的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,烦恼的时候就得找神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:04.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说 我查了这个岛神社的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不愧是五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,老奶奶 您知道哪个神社比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这四座都适合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,四名少女出现在海的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在猫的石舞台上起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是很久以前岛上流传下来的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:26.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你还要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:33.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这种地方遇到珍奇的传说神社真是太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜托那座神社的话就解决啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明天去参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就这么定了 快去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,熬夜可是美容的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,睡眠是人生一大宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,早睡早起 参拜神社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,老奶奶 感谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是这儿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,五十铃 说到参拜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,行一礼后再进 不能走参道的正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:13.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,祭拜的是招财猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望猫咪们能回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一百万日元的香钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是理解不了这行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们也来参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要尊从礼法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:44.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为嘛要给供奉的神献酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,该供的应该是高汤乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不对 是酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就像故乡奈良的石舞台一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,石舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家来摸摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神社的石头摸了的话会有好事发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,除了用手摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还有浇上水会出现鹤纹龟纹的鹤龟石头什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,老奶奶说的石舞台会不会就是这块石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神社供的对象有可能就是这块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用水清洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,樱子 过来看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:31.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就好像樱子说的鹤龟石一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望猫咪们能回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里也有石舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,文字是S
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,North South 北和南
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,指的是方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,难道是五行思想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那接下来是E和W 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望猫咪们能回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,文字出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么 不一样的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 不是E或W吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神社谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快去下一个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,S
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是首字母吗 想表达些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谜团越来越复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:37.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 为什么四个神社的石头上会都有记号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,像阴阳道的四神那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:46.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,净是乌冬 而且还都是同一种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这岛上的乌冬 不得了 美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那位老奶奶会不会知道些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:53.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,去美味乌冬那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看到了奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:07.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那是前天晚上去看海的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在岩石后面 有人在给猫咪喂食
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,旁边停着船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:18.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫咪们在烟的笼罩下朝着船走了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,想要确认探出身的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那肯定是猫妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫…猫妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,果然还是心情不好 不肯跟我们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的只要一起玩了就会告诉我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么都会告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫老大可是岛上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么接下来就交给姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来啊来啊 一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看这里看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这边 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫老大酱 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,忍耐对身体不好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:19.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来来来来来来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,接下来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个味道是木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 跑过来的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠姐 静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神仙保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,肚子好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,眼睛闭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就是夏月的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,昨天还在哭的孩子们都已经笑开了花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月真是让别人露出笑容的天才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个味道是木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的是神仙保佑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:53.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那副眼镜和刚才说烟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:58.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看来猫妖的真正身份就是猫嶋议员了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:03.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想把猫咪们叫回岛上 有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,樱子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:12.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,时间正好 接下来我们要去吃美味乌冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家也请一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:19.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个 我们现在在想如何才能把猫咪们带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,首先让我们吃乌冬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,味道有我樱子保证 肯定好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:32.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们的党首说出去的话就不会收回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就请一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,到时再听听各位想说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:42.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,姐姐 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来份乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 我们的乌冬呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:00.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,老奶奶 这个记号肯定有什么意义对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,比如把猫咪们叫回来的暗示什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:07.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个岛上有一个很久以前流传下来的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,岛上的猫消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,四位少女从海的对面出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在猫的石舞台跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:24.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么只要有少女 猫就会回来了吧
